title: SwiftTEA: Wildest Dreams (Taylor's Version)
description:
What is Taylor doing to us all? We're personally in the Lover era after wrapping up the Fearless era and while waiting for Red TV.. and then she drops a song from 1989 on us? Our emotions are exploding.. but she had a very good reason for doing this! Get the scoop now in this emergency edition of SwifTEA!

What did we miss? What would you like to hear next? There are lots of ways to contact us!
